0the%20third%20accused%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Zone%204%2C%20Panna%20Momaya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2013%2C%20Chaurasia%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20law%20student%20from%20Prayagraj%2C%20crashed%20the%20Volkswagen%20Virtus%20sedan%20he%20was%20driving%20into%20three%20vehicles%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20death%20of%20one%20woman%2C%20Hemali%20Patel.%20The%20incident%2C%20captured%20on%20camera%2C%20took%20place%20near%20Amrapali%20Chaar%20Rasta%20in%20Karelibag%2C%20a%20busy%20intersection%20in%20Vadodara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20accused's%20disturbing%20reaction%20had%20gone%20viral%20in%20which%20the%20accused%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20black%20T-shirt%2C%20repeatedly%20shouted%3A%20%26quot%3BAnother%20round%2C%20another%20round!%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BOm%20Namah%20Shivay!%26quot%3B%20(a%20religious%20chant).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20a%20day%20later%20and%20charged%20with%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20who%20was%20studying%20at%20the%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20University%20of%20Baroda%2C%20earlier%20denied%20being%20drunk%20or%20speeding%20and%20attributed%20the%20crash%20to%20the%20car's%20airbags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20overtaking%20a%20scooter%20and%20turned%20right%20when%20we%20hit%20a%20pothole.%20The%20car%20touched%20another%20vehicle%2C%20and%20the%20airbag%20deployed%2C%20impairing%20my%20vision%20and%20causing%20the%20car%20to%20go%20out%20of%20control...I%20was%20told%20that%20a%20woman%20died%20and%20others%20were%20injured.%20I%20want%20to%20meet%20the%20victims'%20families%20--%20it%20is%20my%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743819300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frjnosjg8_rakshit-chaurasia-split_625x300_16_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvadodara-cr