0his%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20unveiled%20his%20barrage%20of%20import%20duties%20against%20dozens%20of%20countries%20Wednesday%2C%20was%20unrepentant%2C%20posting%20that%20%26quot%3Bmy%20policies%20will%20never%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20get%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20Republican%2C%20who%20was%20spending%20a%20long%20weekend%20golfing%20at%20his%20course%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20theory%20that%20the%20might%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20will%20force%20foreign%20companies%20to%20manufacture%20on%20US%20soil%2C%20rather%20than%20continue%20to%20import%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BONLY%20THE%20WEAK%20WILL%20FAIL!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20touted%20in%20one%20more%20Truth%20Social%20post%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20yet%20another%2C%20he%20insisted%20corporations%20were%20unfazed.%20%26quot%3BBig%20business%20is%20not%20worried%20about%20the%20Tariffs%2C%20because%20they%20know%20they%20are%20here%20to%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20however%2C%20responded%20by%20announcing%20its%20own%20new%2034-percent%20tariffs%20on%20US%20imports%20starting%20April%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20said%20it%20would%20sue%20the%20United%20States%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20and%20also%20restrict%20export%20of%20rare%20earth%20elements%20used%20in%20high-end%20medical%20and%20electronics%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20big%20US%20trading%20partners%20held%20back%20as%20they%20digested%20the%20unfolding%20international%20standoff%20and%20fears%20of%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20trade%20chief%20Maros%20Sefcovic%20said%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20which%20Trump%20hit%20with%20a%2020-percent%20tariff%2C%20will%20act%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20calm%2C%20carefully%20phased%2C%20unified%20way%2