%20it%20would%20increase%20its%20US%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'He's%20out%20golfing!'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Senator%20Amy%20Klobuchar%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20tariffs%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20hurt%20regular%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20%26quot%3Bmessing%20around%20with%20people's%20lives...%20while%20he's%20out%20golfing!%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20was%20rare%20criticism%20from%20the%20right%20too%2C%20with%20Trump%20loyalist%20Republican%20Senator%20Ted%20Cruz%20worrying%20that%20the%20tariffs%20could%20%26quot%3Bhurt%20jobs%20and%20hurt%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20chairman's%20speech%20also%20highlighted%20concerns%20that%20the%20shockwaves%20will%20reach%20deep%20into%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20minutes%20before%20Powell%20suggested%20the%20Fed%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20off%20from%20cutting%20its%20benchmark%20lending%20rate%2C%20Trump%20pressured%20him%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCUT%20INTEREST%20RATES%2C%20JEROME%2C%20AND%20STOP%20PLAYING%20POLITICS!%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20--%20once%20again%20defying%20the%20longstanding%20White%20House%20custom%20of%20respecting%20the%20central%20bank's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20more%20concrete%20sign%20of%20how%20tariffs%20are%20impacting%20trade%2C%20Nintendo%20announced%20it%20was%20delaying%20preorders%20of%20its%20hotly%20anticipated%20Switch%202%20gaming%20console%20while%20it%20assesses%20%26quot%3Bevolving%26quot%3B%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743816240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fsotvfl3k_donald-trump-xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_26_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%