%20deadline%20for%20TikTok%20to%20find%20a%20non-Chinese%20buyer%20or%20face%20a%20ban%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20allowing%2075%20more%20days%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Administration%20has%20been%20working%20very%20hard%20on%20a%20deal%20to%20save%20TikTok%2C%20and%20we%20have%20made%20tremendous%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20deadline%20was%20to%20expire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20transaction%20requires%20more%20work%20to%20ensure%20all%20necessary%20approvals%20are%20signed%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20am%20signing%20an%20Executive%20Order%20to%20keep%20TikTok%20up%20and%20running%20for%20an%20additional%2075%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hugely%20popular%20video-sharing%20app%2C%20which%20has%20more%20than%20170%20million%20American%20users%2C%20is%20under%20threat%20from%20a%20US%20law%20passed%20last%20year%20that%20orders%20TikTok%20to%20split%20from%20its%20Chinese%20owner%20ByteDance%20or%20get%20shut%20down%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20insisted%20his%20administration%20is%20near%20a%20deal%20to%20find%20a%20buyer%20for%20TikTok%20and%20keep%20it%20from%20shutting%20down%20that%20would%20involve%20multiple%20investors%2C%20but%20has%20given%20few%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByteDance%2C%20while%20confirming%20that%20it%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20US%20government%20towards%20finding%20a%20solution%2C%20warned%20that%20there%20remained%20%26quot%3Bkey%20matters%26quot%3B%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20agreement%20has%20not%20been%20executed%26quot%3B%20and%20whatever%20was%20decided%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bsubject%20to%20approval%20under%20Chinese%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotivated%20by%20national%20security%20fears%20and%20belief%20in%20Washington%20that%20TikTok%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20the%20ban%20took%20effect%20on%20January%2019%2C%20one%20day%20before%20Trump's%20inauguration%2C%20with%20ByteDance%20having%20made%20no%20attempt%20to%20find%20a%20suitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20temporarily%20shut%20down%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20disappeared%20from%20app%20stores%2C%20to%20the%20dismay%20of%20millions%20of%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Republican%20president%20quickly%20announced%20an%20initial%2075-day%20delay%20and%20TikTok%20was%20restored%20to%20users%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20Apple%20and%20Google%20app%20stores%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%2075-day%20delay%20pushes%20the%20deadline%20to%20June%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20downplayed%20risks%20that%20TikTok%20is%20in%20danger%2C%20saying%20he%20remains%20confident%20of%20finding%20a%20buyer%20for%20the%20app's%20US%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20added%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20working%20in%20good%20faith%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20whose%20government%20will%20need%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20suggested%20TikTok%20could%20even%20be%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20deal%20with%20China%20to%20ease%20the%20stinging%20tariffs%20he%20imposed%20on%20Beijing%20as%20part%20of%20a%20worldwide%20blitz%20of%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20TikTok%20to%20'go%20dark.'%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20TikTok%20and%20China%20to%20close%20the%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20solution%20in%20the%20works%20would%20see%20existing%20US%20investors%20in%20ByteDance%20roll%20over%20their%20stakes%20into%20a%20new%20independent%20global%20TikTok%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20US%20investors%2C%20including%20Oracle%20and%20Blackstone%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20would%20be%20brought%20on%20to%20reduce%20ByteDance's%20share%20in%20the%20new%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20TikTok's%20US%20activity%20is%20already%20housed%20on%20Oracle%20servers%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20chairman%2C%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20is%20a%20longtime%20Trump%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20reported%20on%20Friday%20that%20Walmart%20was%20also%20in%20the%20mix%2C%20spurred%20on%20by%20a%20late%20expression%20of%20interest%20by%20retail%20archrival%20Amazon%20to%20buy%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalmart%20and%20Oracle%20were%20previously%20rumored%20to%20be%20buying%20TikTok%20in%20the%20US%20when%20Trump%20tried%20to%20wrest%20the%20company%20from%20its%20Chinese%20owners%20during%20his%20first%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20long%20supported%20a%20ban%20or%20divestment%2C%20but%20has%20lately%20defended%20TikTok%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20reason%20more%20young%20voters%20supported%20him%20in%20November's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20What%20about%20the%20algorithm%3F%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20remains%2C%20particularly%20over%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20TikTok's%20valuable%20algorithm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok%20without%20its%20algorithm%20is%20like%20Harry%20Potter%20without%20his%20wand%20--%20it's%20simply%20not%20as%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Forrester%20Principal%20Analyst%20Kelsey%20Chickering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20media%20reports%20suggest%20the%20new%20company%20could%20license%20the%20algorithm%20from%20ByteDance%2C%20which%20would%20remain%20invested%20in%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20an%20arrangement%20would%20go%20against%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20law%2C%20which%20is%20in%20part%20based%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20TikTok's%20algorithm%20can%20be%20weaponized%20by%20the%20Chinese%20against%20US%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%