3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c023f7d-acdd-4166-8e81-0572ea0f22da%5C%22%3EPerimenopause%20left%20me%20drained%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20age%20of%2043%2C%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fperimenopause-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiencing%20perimenopausal%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20starting%20with%20sudden%20episodes%20of%20unexplained%20rage.%20Over%20time%2C%20these%20symptoms%20expanded%20to%20include%20irregular%20bleeding%2C%20severe%20fatigue%2C%20and%20debilitating%20migraines.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20simply%20getting%20out%20of%20bed%20felt%20impossible%2C%20deeply%20affecting%20my%20daily%20life%20and%20emotional%20health.%20Negative%20self-talk%20about%20my%20body%20and%20health%20further%20intensified%20my%20struggles%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2045%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20all%20the%20years%20before%20perimenopause%20that%20I%20had%20felt%20well%20nearly%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20health%20issues%2C%20was%20on%20no%20medication%2C%20and%20felt%20good%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20all%20I%20focused%20on%20was%20my%20weight.%20I%20spent%20my%20%26quot%3Bgood%20years%26quot%3B%20ungrateful%20for%20the%20body%20I'd%20had%20%E2%80%94%20only%20concerned%20with%20how%20I%20looked%2C%20thinking%20beauty%20was%20only%20to%20be%20found%20in%20being%20a%20certain%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20watched%20my%20dad%20regret%20taking%20all%20those%20younger%20years%20of%20his%20life%20for%20granted%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20didn't%20do%20the%20same.%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbe-grateful-to-yourself-to-achieve-goals-faster-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciate%20the%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20my%20body%20is%20currently%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20what%20I%20don't%20like%20abou