with%20amenities.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22outlets%20and%20lights%20on%20a%20premium%20cabin%20seat%20on%20a%20kenya%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1c0b369253ccddf990566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20my%20own%20outlets%20at%20my%20seat.%3Cp%3ESuzie%20Dundas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20premium%20seat%20came%20with%20a%20large%20side%20table%20with%20USB%20ports%20and%20a%20standard%20(Kenyan)%20plug%2C%20an%20adjustable%20reading%20light%2C%20a%20small%20storage%20compartment%2C%20a%20screen%20with%20seat%20controls%2C%20and%20a%20footrest.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20large%20TV%20screen%20and%20plenty%20of%20space%20in%20the%20overhead%20bin%20for%20my%20large%20backpack%20and%20overstuffed%20duffel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20recommend%20choosing%20a%20seat%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20train%20if%20you're%20on%20this%20route.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22look%20out%20the%20windows%20on%20a%20kenya%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1c0f3b8b41a9673fa6b9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20saw%20wildlife%20right%20from%20the%20train.%3Cp%3ESuzie%20Dundas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20seat%20was%20tilted%20slightly%20to%20the%20left%2C%20which%20left%20my%20back%20a%20little%20more%20exposed%20to%20the%20aisle.%20The%20angled%20seating%20felt%20odd%20at%20first.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20once%20the%20train%20started%20moving%2C%20the%20design%20made%20more%20sense.%20Passengers%20on%20the%20left%20side%20got%20a%20direct%2C%20unobstructed%20view%20of%20the%20landscape%20without%20needing%20to%20turn%20their%20heads.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20train%20also%20had%20great%20views%2C%20those%20passengers%20had%20to%20twist%20a%20bit%20more%20to%20take%20in%20the%20scenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sleeping%20situation%20felt%20as%20nice%20as%20a%20first-class%20flight.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22seat%20recliner%20buttons%20on%20a%20train%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1c136b8b41a9673fa6bab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20could%20lay%20all%20the%20way%20back.%3Cp%3ESuzie%20Dundas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20flown%20first%20class%20on%20international%20flights%20before%2C%20and%20this%20train%20felt%20just%20as%20nice%20as%20those%20trips.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lie-flat%20seat%20controls%20worked%20well%2C%20and%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20footrest%20extension%2C%20my%20entire%20setup%20became%20a%20continuous%20sleeping%20surface.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%205%20feet%2C%207%20inches%2C%20I%20could%20fully%20stretch%20out%20%E2%80%94%20but%20taller%20passengers%20might%20need%20to%20bend%20their%20legs%20slightly.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20meal%20was%20so-so%2C%20but%20it%20still%20added%20to%20the%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meal%20on%20a%20kenya%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1c1a1b8b41a9673fa6bc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20got%20breakfast%20on%20the%20train.%3Cp%3ESuzie%20Dundas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBreakfast%20service%20began%20soon%20after%20I%20boarded.%20Train%20attendants%20came%20around%20to%20take%20my%20order%20from%20three%20meal%20options%3A%20Indian%2C%20Kenyan%2C%20or%20Western.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20scrambled%20eggs%20with%20tomatoes%20and%20yogurt.%20Although%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20the%20meal%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20my%20ride%2C%20it%20helped%20the%20trip%20feel%20more%20el