of%20the%20plastic%20particles%20they%20detected%20had%20already%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20simple%20way%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20plastic%20is%20to%20chew%20your%20gum%20for%20longer%20instead%20of%20popping%20a%20new%20piece%2C%20Lisa%20Lowe%2C%20a%20graduate%20student%20who%20ran%20this%20study%20with%20Mohanty%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acs.org%2Fpressroom%2Fpresspacs%2F2025%2Fmarch%2Fchewing-gum-can-shed-microplastics-into-saliva-pilot-study-finds.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20your%20daily%20microplastic%20ingestion%2C%20a%20stick%20of%20gum%20probably%20isn't%20much.%20You%20ingest%20billions%20more%20microplastics%20from%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20made%20with%20a%20plastic-containing%20teabag%20(which%20is%20more%20common%20than%20you%20might%20think)%2C%20a%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0045653524026377%23sec3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20a%20gum-chewing%20habit%20could%20add%20up.%20Based%20on%20their%20findings%2C%20the%20researchers%20calculated%20that%20someone%20who%20chews%20160%20to%20180%20small%20sticks%20of%20gum%20per%20year%20would%20ingest%20about%2030%2C000%20microplastic%20particles%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMohanty%20said%20his%20wife%20stopped%20chewing%20gum%20altogether%20after%20hearing%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20eat%20chewing%20gum%20and%20directly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-from-nonstick-cookware-may-end-up-in-food-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eingest%20plastics%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Chewing%20gum%20is%20non-essential%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohanty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%20chew%2C%20Mohanty%20added%2C%20throw%20your%20gum%20in%20the%20garbage%20instead%20of%20leaving%20chewed-up%20plastic%20in%20the