3Cp%3EHaving%20some%20of%20your%20investments%20in%20cash%20or%20cash%20equivalents%2C%20like%20a%20money%20market%20fund%2C%20is%20important.%20Whether%20saving%20for%20an%20emergency%20or%20looking%20to%20deploy%20it%20into%20future%20investments%2C%20holding%20cash%20ultimately%20protects%20from%20some%20of%20the%20downside%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20big%20plunge%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20outside%20of%20a%20recession%2C%20you%20should%20aim%20to%20have%20an%20amount%20of%20cash%20on%20hand%20to%20fund%20at%20least%20six%20months%20of%20your%20expenses%2C%20or%20if%20you%20are%20retired%20and%20don't%20have%20employment%20income%20to%20support%20your%20spending%2C%20perhaps%20up%20to%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Brett%20Panziera%2C%20CFP%2C%20an%20associate%20director%20of%20financial%20planning%20at%20EP%20Wealth%20Advisors%2C%20told%20BI's%20Fox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-what-to-do-investing-trade-war-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743796995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b0d71c393cd3c8629b4415%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-what-to-do-investing-trade-war-tariffs-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fear%20is%20running%20high%20amid%20the%20worst%20stock%20sell-off%20in%20years.%20It's%20important%20for%20investors%20not%20to%20panic%20as%20they%20watch%20their%20portfolios%20take%20a%20hit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22madams%40businessinsider.com%20(Max%20Adams)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A129%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-what-to-do-investing-trade-war-tariffs-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Stop%20playing%20politics!%E2%80%99%3A%20Trump%20urges%20Fed%20Chair%