2%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20trade%20is%20unraveling%20in%20the%20sweeping%20turmoil%20in%20global%20markets%2C%20with%20stocks%20acutely%20exposed%20to%20the%20US%20economy%20sinking%20alongside%20the%20dollar.%20As%20Wall%20Street's%20rebellion%20against%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20war%20intensifies%2C%20traders%20are%20rushing%20into%20fixed-income%20havens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20%242%20trillion%20was%20erased%20from%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20with%20the%20gauge%20down%20about%205%25.%20The%20Russell%202000%20of%20smaller%20firms%20extended%20its%20plunge%20from%20a%202021%20all-time%20high%20to%2020%25%20on%20speculation%20the%20president's%20trade%20offensive%20will%20stunt%20the%20American%20economy.%20The%20greenback%20slid%201.5%25%2C%20reigniting%20the%20debate%20about%20its%20haven%20reputation%20during%20challenging%20times%20as%20the%20euro%2C%20yen%20and%20Swiss%20franc%20surged.%20Oil%20joined%20a%20selloff%20in%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%2C%20the%20much-vaunted%20America-first%20trade%20-%20buying%20up%20assets%20that%20win%20when%20the%20US%20outperforms%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20-%20is%20reversing%20on%20concern%20that%20the%20steepest%20increase%20in%20American%20tariffs%20in%20a%20century%20will%20hammer%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20driving%20a%20fierce%20rally%20in%20global%20bonds%2C%20sending%20the%20yield%20on%20benchmark%20Treasuries%20briefly%20below%20the%20closely-watched%204%25%20level.%20Most%20other%20yields%20also%20tumbled%20as%20money%20markets%20priced%20in%20a%2050%25%20chance%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20delivering%20four%20quarter-point%20rate%20reductions%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20embraced%20tariffs%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20assert%20US%20power%2C%20revive%20manufacturing%20at%20home%20and%20extract%20geopolitical%20concessions.%20Economists%20say%20the%20near-term%20result%20of%20his%20measures%20will%20likely%20be%20higher%