an%2C%20and%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliates-own-tariffs-against-trump-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20hit%20particularly%20hard%20because%20Trump's%20latest%20round%20of%20tariffs%20was%20combined%20with%20existing%20ones%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20to%2054%25.%20Stocks%20continued%20to%20crater%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20the%20Dow%20down%20roughly%204%25%20as%20of%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b81d5bf-b087-45d4-8b5a-00847c122bf3%5C%22%3EIt's%20California%20v.%20Trump%2C%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENewsom's%20comments%20reignite%20the%20long-running%20feud%20between%20the%20nation's%20most%20populous%20state%20and%20Trump.%20The%20White%20House%20wasted%20little%20time%20firing%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGavin%20Newsom%20should%20focus%20on%20out-of-control%20homelessness%2C%20crime%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20unaffordability%20in%20California%20instead%20of%20trying%20his%20hand%20at%20international%20dealmaking%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Kush%20Desai%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20potential%202028%20challenger%2C%20Newsom%20is%20also%20coming%20close%20to%2C%20if%20not%20outright%20crossing%2C%20the%20legal%20line%20between%20federal%20and%20state%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20first%20administration%20sued%20California%20after%20then-Gov.%20Jerry%20Brown%20brokered%20a%20climate%20change%20agreement%20with%20the%20Canadian%20province%20of%20Qu%C3%A9bec%20after%20Trump%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20pull%20the%20US%20out%20of%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Accord.%20California%20won%20at%20the%20lower-court%20level%2C%20but%20the%20dispute%20was%20never%20fully%20resolved%20when%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Justice%20Department%20dropped%20the%20case%20in%20April%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ab2f532-7e81-4c47-96d3-a63acabdc391%5C%22%3ENewsom%20is%20on%20dicey%