xperiences%2C%20so%20I%20was%20open%20to%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20priority%20filter%20was%20departure%20and%20arrival%20time.%20I%20wanted%20something%20that%20wouldn't%20interfere%20with%20my%20work%20schedule.%20That%20meant%20that%20the%20earliest%20flight%20I%20could%20take%20on%20a%20weekday%20would%20depart%20by%207%20p.m.%20and%20the%20latest%20would%20arrive%20by%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20those%20filters%2C%20and%20while%20playing%20with%20Google%20Flights'%20different%20filters%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20price%20comparison%20tools%20for%20the%20first%20week%20of%20April%2C%20a%20surprising%20price%20appeared%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one-way%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eflight%20from%20Miami%20to%20Newark%20was%20listed%20as%20%2410%2C%20although%20booking%20options%20showed%20that%20the%20total%20would%20actually%20be%20%2420%20if%20booked%20through%20the%20airline's%20website%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20was%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20Miami%20at%209%3A51%20p.m.%20and%20arrive%20in%20New%20Jersey%20at%2012%3A59%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20be%20flexible%20in%20my%20schedule%20and%20get%20the%20best%20deal%20on%20my%20return%20flight%20as%20well%2C%20so%20I%20waited%20until%20later%20to%20book%20my%20return%2C%20which%20I%20would%20also%20buy%20as%20a%20one-way%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20first%20I%20wasn't%20too%20trusting%20of%20the%20third-party%20website%2C%20but%20I%20booked%20it%20anyway.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Confirmation%20screen%20for%20%2410%20Spirit%20Airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eed2ddb8b41a9673fc9492%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20booked%20the%20flight%20after%20reading%20reviews%20of%20the%20third-party%20website%20online.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third-party%20website%20offering%20the%20%2410%20fare%20was%20called%20eDreams.%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20there%20were%20risks%20associated%20with%20booking%20through%20third-party%20retailers.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20the%20airline%20cancels%20or%20delays%20the%20flight%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20get%20a%20refund%20or%20reach%20a%20customer%20service%20representative.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20looking%20up%20reviews%20on%20forum%20websites%20like%20Reddit%20and%20Quora%2C%20I%20figured%20it%20was%20safe%20enough%20to%20book%20the%20flight%20through%20them.%20After%20all%2C%20if%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20phony%2C%20it%20would%20only%20be%20a%20%2410%20gamble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccepting%20the%20risk%20of%20booking%20through%20a%20third-party%20website%2C%20which%20I%20had%20never%20done%20for%20flights%20before%2C%20I%20bought%20my%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20confirmed%2C%20the%20flight%20seemed%20legit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Confirmation%20for%20%2410%20Spirit%20airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeebb163d72727e1992670%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20email%20from%20the%20airline%20was%20exactly%20like%20the%20ones%20I%20had%20received%20before%20when%20booking%20through%20them%20directly.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20airline's%20confirmation%20email%2C%20my%20initial%20doubts%20faded.%20The%20email%20looked%20like%20others%20I%20had%20received%20before.%20Plus%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20log%20into%20my%20account%20with%20the%20airline%20and%20see%20the%20upcoming%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20curious%20that%20on%20Spirit's%20confirmation%20email%2C%20the%20total%20for%20the%20flight%20was%20different%20than%20what%20I%20actually%20paid.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20only%20%249.97%20left%20my%20bank%20account%2C%20in%20the%20email%2C%20Spirit%20listed%20the%20total%20as%20%2419.30%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20what%20it%20would've%20cost%20to%20book%20through%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20could%20only%20bring%20a%20personal%20item.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flight%20information%20on%20confirmation%20email.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeec56b8b41a9673fc9a77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221224%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20my%20basic%20economy%20flight%2C%20I%20could%20opt%20to%20check%20a%20bag%20or%20select%20a%20seat%20for%20an%20extra%20fee.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20flight%20was%20confirmed%2C%20I%20reviewed%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20ultra-cheap%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20airline's%20basic%20economy%20option%2C%20I%20wasn't%20allowed%20to%20bring%20a%20carry-on%20bag%2C%20although%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fairline-baggage-fees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecked%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20available%20for%20purchase%20for%20%2475.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommitted%20to%20traveling%20on%20as%20low%20a%20budget%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20only%20bring%20with%20me%20a%20personal%20item%20bag%2C%20which%20I%20was%20allowed.%20The%20bag%2C%20defined%20a%20backpack%20or%20a%20laptop%20bag%2C%20needed%20to%20fit%20under%20the%20seat%20on%20the%20airplane%2C%20measuring%2018%20x%2014%20x%208%20inches%20at%20a%20maximum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20the%20size%20limitation%2C%20I%20had%20to%20be%20strategic%20about%20what%20I%20packed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223519%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I%20bought%20an%20efficient%20carry-on%20personal%20item%20bag%20on%20Amazon%20that%20measures%20exactly%20as%20much%20as%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20bring.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9dbb63d72727e199160e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222631%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bag%20fits%20comfortably%20within%20the%20size%20limitations%20and%20can%20extend%20for%20extra%20space.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPreparing%20for%20a%2010-day%20trip%2C%20I%20had%20to%20strategize%20how%20I%20used%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-personal-item-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20item%20luggage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20%2422%20bag%20on%20Amazon%20that%20had%20come%20up%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20TikTok%20feed.%20Users%20recommended%20it%20as%20a%20travel%20bag%2C%20and%20it%20fit%20within%20the%20airline's%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20expandable%20bag%20should%20fit%20comfortably%20within%20the%20measurements%2C%20I%20was%20scared%20that%20expanding%20the%20bottom%20by%20a%20few%20inches%20would%20make%20it%20larger%20than%20what%20was%20acceptable%20to%20bring%20aboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20nervous%20about%20over-stuffing%20the%20bag.%20I%20had%20previously%20read%20reports%20of%20airline%20agents%20deciding%20personal%20item%20bags%20were%20too%20big%20at%20the%20door%20and%20charging%20an%20additional%20fee%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-airlines-charging-check-bags-first-time-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry-on%20luggage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20I%20had%20never%20had%20that%20happen%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWary%20of%20how%20I%20utilized%20space%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20pack%20only%20the%20necessities%20and%20keep%20items%20in%20mind%20I%20could%20take%20out%20if%20needed%20to%20close%20the%20extended%20compartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20packed%20a%20capsule%20wardrobe%20with%20work%20and%20casual%20outfits.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Packed%20luggage%20for%20a%20week-long%20work%20trip%20on%20a%20personal%20item%20bag.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9d48b8b41a9673fc8a06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20packed%20all%20the%20essentials%20I%20needed%20for%20a%2010-day%20trip%20inside%20the%20personal-item-sized%20bag.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20trip%20schedule%20revolving%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwhere-to-shop-for-womens-workwear-clothes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20meeting%20up%20with%20friends%20in%20the%20city%20after%20work%2C%20I%20packed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fmarcella-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapsule%20wardrobe%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20outfits%20I%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstyle-tips-day-to-night-work-outfits-spring-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edress%20up%20or%20down%20during%20the%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20a%20limited%20color%20palette%20that%20could%20be%20worn%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20using%20green%20as%20the%20signature%20color%20and%20light%20and%20dark%20neutrals%20as%20the%20bulk%20of%20what%20I%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%2010%20days%2C%20I%20packed%20four%20white%20tops%20and%20blouses%2C%20four%20darker%20tops%20and%20blouses%2C%20three%20work%20pants%20(black%2C%20cream%2C%20and%20khaki)%2C%20two%20skirts%20(grey%20and%20green)%2C%20one%20workout%20set%2C%20two%20pairs%20of%20comfortable%2C%20office-friendly%20shoes%2C%20one%20pair%20of%20sneakers%2C%20a%20big%20work%20bag%2C%20and%20a%20smaller%20purse%20for%20going%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kept%20toiletries%20and%20electronics%20to%20a%20minimum%2C%20only%20bringing%20products%20in%20small%20pouches%20and%20limiting%20myself%20to%20one%20small%20bag%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20makeup%20and%20toiletries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20packed%20strategically%2C%20putting%20all%20the%20shoes%20at%20the%20bottom%20and%20fitting%20socks%20in%20between%20them%2C%20then%20arranging%20clothes%20in%20space-saving%20ways%20and%20using%20the%20purse%20for%20extra%20storage%20space%20within%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wore%20the%20other%20half%20of%20my%20luggage%20to%20the%20airport.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author's%20outfit%20at%20the%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea839b8b41a9673fc8bde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20bring%20seven%20extra%20items%20I%20couldn't%20fit%20in%20the%20small%20bag%20by%20wearing%20them%20to%20the%20airport.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20my%20bulkiest%20items%20and%20layering%20for%20maximized%20stuff-bringing%2C%20I%20layered%20my%20workout%20set%20under%20a%20pair%20of%20wide-leg%20jeans%20and%20a%20thick%20knit%20sweater%2C%20which%20I%20topped%20with%20a%20leather%20blazer%20(with%20books%20and%20other%20essentials%20in%20every%20pocket).%20I%20also%20wore%20a%20pair%20of%20boots%20and%20a%20scarf%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outfit%20was%20efficient%20and%20beyond%20well%20equipped%20for%20the%2045-degree%20weather%20waiting%20for%20me%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20but%20it%20was%20certainly%20too%20hot%20for%20the%2079-degree%20Miami%20that%20I%20was%20departing.%20I%20ended%20up%20taking%20off%20the%20scarf%20and%20jacket%20in%20the%20Miami%20airport%20and%20carrying%20them%20along%20with%20me%20during%20the%20flight%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDespite%20carrying%2010%20days%20worth%20of%20clothes%2C%20my%20bag%20fit%20in%20the%20personal%20item%20bin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20bag%20fit%20perfectly%20in%20the%20personal%20item%20slot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9deb69253ccddf9b2377%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20overstuffed%20bag%20might've%20needed%20a%20push%20to%20fit%2C%20but%20nevertheless%2C%20it%20met%20the%20requirements.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20much%20anticipation%20and%20preparation%20%E2%80%94%20including%20arriving%20at%20the%20airport%20extra%20early%2C%20identifying%20items%20I'd%20be%20OK%20leaving%20behind%20and%20asking%20my%20ride%20to%20wait%20until%20I%20could%20confirm%20my%20bag%20fit%20%E2%80%94%20I%20dropped%20my%20slightly%20overstuffed%20bag%20carrying%2010%20days%20worth%20of%20clothes%20into%20the%20measuring%20bin.%20It%20fit!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20might've%20had%20to%20push%20it%20down%20into%20the%20compartment%20quite%20a%20bit%20in%20order%20for%20it%20to%20fit%2C%20but%20after%20getting%20a%20thumbs-up%20from%20an%20airline%20agent%2C%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way%20to%20check%20in%20with%20no%20luggage%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECheck-in%20was%20easy%20at%20a%20surprisingly%20quiet%20Miami%20International%20Airport.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nearly%20empty%20hallway%20at%20the%20Miami%20International%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9e7e63d72727e199162a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20usually%20hectic%20airport%20was%20pleasantly%20calm.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20traveled%20out%20of%20Miami%20International%2C%20my%20home%20base%20airport%2C%20dozens%20of%20times%2C%20I%20was%20very%20surprised%20by%20how%20quiet%20and%20empty%20the%20airport%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20have%20been%20the%20departure%20time%20%E2%80%94%20my%20flight%20had%20been%20pushed%20back%20by%20about%20an%20hour%20to%2010%3A50%20p.m.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20middle-of-the-week%20night%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20be%20quieter%2C%20SimpleFlying.com%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20go%20through%20a%20line-less%20TSA%20check-in%20in%20under%2010%20minutes%20made%20my%20travel%20experience%20all%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20the%20staff%20was%20friendly%2C%20and%20the%20aircraft%20was%20clean.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20boarding%20%2410%20Spirit%20Airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea08869253ccddf9b23d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20boarding%20process%20was%20seamless%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20delays%20were%20pushed%20up%2C%20allowing%20for%20an%20earlier%20departure.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20at%20the%20gate%2C%20the%20airline%20personnel%20were%20organized%2C%20friendly%2C%20and%20eager%20to%20start%20a%20conversation.%20One%20flight%20attendant%20asked%20about%20the%20book%20I%20was%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20friendly%20service%20was%20made%20even%20better%20by%20the%20seamless%20boarding%20process%2C%20which%20took%20under%2030%20minutes%20for%20all%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20basic%20economy%2C%20I%20was%20in%20the%20second-to-last%20group%20to%20board.%20Not%20many%20of%20the%20people%20at%20the%20gate%20seemed%20to%20board%20during%20the%20first%20four%20groups%2C%20usually%20reserved%20for%20first-%20and%20business-class%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20seating%2C%20the%20crew%20made%20an%20announcement%20about%20the%20flight%20not%20being%20too%20crowded%20and%20asked%20passengers%20not%20to%20seat%20themselves%20in%20the%20empty%20seats%20for%20weight%20distribution%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20select%20my%20seat%2C%20leaving%20me%20with%20an%20aisle%20seat%20near%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Seats%20at%20Spirit%20Airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eead2bb8b41a9673fc8ce2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20satisfied%20with%20my%20seat%2C%20which%20I%20had%20not%20paid%20extra%20to%20select.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20airline's%20seat%20selection%20option%2C%20as%20it%20came%20with%20an%20extra%20fee%2C%20and%20I%20was%20too%20committed%20to%20traveling%20for%20under%20%2410.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20I%20was%20assigned%20was%20near%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane%20in%20an%20aisle%20seat%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20some%20extra%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20themselves%20weren't%20the%20most%20comfortable%2C%20but%20they%20were%20bearable%20enough%20for%20a%20three-hour%20midnight%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20legroom%20wasn't%20too%20bad%2C%20and%20my%20bag%20comfortably%20fit%20under%20the%20seat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Legroom%20in%20the%20%2410%20Spirit%20Airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9ed169253ccddf9b2396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20feet%20were%20perhaps%20a%20little%20crammed%2C%20being%20unable%20to%20fit%20under%20the%20seat%20with%20my%20bag%20there.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20my%20seat%2C%20I%20put%20my%20personal%20item%20bag%20under%20the%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20made%20myself%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20legroom%20itself%20wasn't%20too%20bad%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20much%20space%20for%20my%20feet%20with%20my%20luggage%20under%20the%20seat.%20Thankfully%2C%20having%20the%20aisle%20seat%20meant%20I%20could%20extend%20my%20legs%20a%20bit%20to%20the%20side%20during%20the%20flight%2C%20making%20it%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20flight%20didn't%20have%20complimentary%20snacks%20or%20drinks%2C%20but%20they%20were%20available%20for%20purchase.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snacks%20menu%20at%20%2410%20Spirit%20Airlines%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee9f46b8b41a9673fc8a6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20eyed%20the%20snacks%20for%20a%20while%20but%20stuck%20to%20my%20extreme%20budget%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20traveling%20for%20%2410.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-vs-delta-basic-economy-review-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic%20economy%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20include%20refreshments%2C%20a%20snack%20and%20menu%20drink%20were%20available%2C%20including%20sweet%20and%20savory%20bites%2C%20soft%20drinks%2C%20and%20alcoholic%20beverages%2C%20as%20well%20as%20packages%20offering%20a%20combination%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20what%20I%20had%20expected%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20the%20items%20were%20good%20and%20not%20too%20inflated%2C%20although%20I%20wish%20they%20had%20been%20included%20with%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnacks%20and%20soft%20drinks%20cost%20between%20%243.35%20and%20%245.49%2C%20and%20alcohol%20ranged%20from%20%249.49%20for%20a%20can%20of%20beer%20to%20%2412.49%20for%20a%20small%20bottle%