0Waqf%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20body%20at%20all.%20It%20is%20a%20legal%20or%20a%20statutory%20body...%20The%20'Muttawali'%20is%20just%20a%20superintendent%20or%20a%20manager.%20He%20does%20not%20have%20any%20rights%20over%20the%20property%2C%20because%20once%20a%20Waqf%20has%20been%20created%2C%20the%20property%20vests%20in%20Allah%2C%20peace%20be%20on%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prasad%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Bill%20will%20empower%20Muslim%20women%20and%20help%20widows%20and%20the%20marginalised%20from%20the%20community.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20pointed%20out%20that%20areas%20near%20the%20Dak%20Bungalow%20locality%20in%20Patna%20%C2%A0-%20the%20city%20he%20is%20from%20-%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20Waqf%20land%20but%20five-star%20hotels%20and%20showrooms%20have%20come%20up%20there.%20He%20also%20said%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20in%20the%20world%20and%20asked%20how%20many%20hospitals%2C%20universities%20and%20training%20centres%20have%20been%20built%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20manager%20using%20the%20property%20the%20way%20the%20person%20who%20dedicated%20it%20intended%20or%20is%20he%20stuffing%20his%20pockets%3F%20That%20is%20the%20question.%20And%20a%20drama%20is%20being%20created%20over%20this...%20Let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20people%20from%20my%20state%20and%20the%20entire%20country%20are%20going%20to%20appreciate%20(this%20Bill).%20People%20were%20dismayed%20to%20learn%20that%20so%20much%20property%20is%20being%20misused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransparency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prasad%20asserted%20that%20the%20bill%20will%20help%20bring%20transparency%20by%20making%20Waqf%20boards%20accountable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20thing%20is%20being%20made%20accountable%2C%20everything%20will%20be%20available%20online%2C%20digitisation%20will%20happen%2C%20you%20can%20see%20which%20property%20is%20where%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Muttawali%2C%20what%20use%20is%20the%20particular%20property%20being%20put%20to%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20'Waqif%20(the%20person%20dedicating%20the%20property).%20So%2C%20all%20these%20things%20are%20very%20transparent%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBacklash%20expected%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20government%20is%20fearing%20some%20kind%20of%20backlash%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20and%20the%20possible%20impact%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20would%20have%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20enjoys%20support%20among%20them%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20polls%20later%20this%20year%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20said%20the%20queries%20around%20Mr%20Kumar%20have%20been%20asked%20since%20he%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%20the%20citizenship%20of%20not%20even%20one%20Muslim%20has%20been%20taken%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20larger%20issue%20is%20we%20were%20two%20in%201984%2C%20just%20two%20(the%20BJP%20had%20two%20seats)%20in%20the%201984%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Where%20are%20we%20today%3F%20Ruling%20the%20country%2C%20in%20more%20than%2021%20states%20of%20the%20country.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20our%20very%20proud%20colleague%20and%20friend%2C%20has%20been%20a%20chief%20minister%20for%2019%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20law%20minister%20also%20insisted%20that%20India's%20polity%20has%20undergone%20a%20'tectonic%20metamorphosis'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...whereas%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20argument%20is%20the%20same.%20Secular%2C%20communal%2C%20appeasement.%20The%20world%20has%20changed.%20India%20has%20changed.%20And%20I%20would%20say%20the%20young%20people%20of%20the%20minority%20community%20and%20the%20thinking%20community%20have%20also%20changed...%20And%20some%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20frustrate%20that%20change%20by%20the%20same%20logic%20of%20the%201990s%20and%201980s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743790800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fbojs1u7_ravi-shankar-prasad-interview_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-bjp-no-mosques-will-be-touched-bjps-ravi-shankar-prasad-on-waqf-bill-8089460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20cleared%20by%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20after%20heated%2C%20marathon%20debates%2C%20will%20benefit%20women%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20and%20ensure%20transparency%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-bjp-no-mosques-will-be-touched-bjps-ravi-shankar-prasad-on-waqf-bill-8089460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump's%20Tariffs%20Are%20Crushing%20Apple's%20'Make%20In%20India'%20Dream%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20quest%20to%20become%20a%20major%20iPhone%20manufacturing%20hub%20has%20encountered%20a%20significant%20obstacle.%20The%20US%20has%20imposed%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20on%20over%20180%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%20which%20has%20been%20slapped%20with%20a%2026%25%20tariff.%20Although%20this%20rate%20is%20lower%20than%20China's%2054%25%20and%20Vietnam's%2046%25%2C%20Indian%20officials%20are%20still%20concerned%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20country's%20electronics%20manufacturing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner%2C%20accounting%20for%2018%25%20of%20total%20goods%20exports.%20The%2026%25%20tariff%20could%20severely%20affect%20electronics%20shipments%2C%20profitability%2C%20and%20supply%20chains.%20Per%20a%20Doordarshan%20news%20report%2C%20Ashok%20Chandak%2C%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Electronics%20and%20Semiconductor%20Association%20(IESA)%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20tariff%20regime%20poses%20a%20significant%20challenge%20to%20India's%20exports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%2026%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20present%20a%20significant%20challenge%20to%20India's%20exports...%20While%20India%20is%20better%20positioned%20than%20many%20other%20economies%2C%20these%20tariffs%20can%20potentially%20impact%20domestic%20industries%2C%20disrupt%20trade%20flows%2C%20and%20squeeze%20profit%20margins%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20which%20has%20relocated%2015%25%20of%20its%20iPhone%20production%20to%20India%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20tariffs.%20The%20company%20faces%20a%2054%25%20duty%20on%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20prices.%20Analysts%20estimate%20that%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max%20could%20cost%20nearly%20%242%2C300%20or%20%E2%82%B91.9%20lakh%20in%20Indian%20terms%20if%20Apple%20passes%20on%20the%20added%20costs%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Apple%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20developments%20related%20to%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20its%20stock%20plunged%20more%20than%208%25%20after%20the%20announcement%20-%20its%20worst%20single%20day%20drop%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20India%20remains%20an%20attractive%20destination%20for%20multinational%20companies%20looking%20to%20diversify%20their%20manufacturing%20operations.%20Apple%20has%20been%20increasing%20its%20footprint%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20government%20is%20hoping%20to%20leverage%20this%20moment%20to%20fast-track%20a%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupport%20from%20corporations%20such%20as%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%20may%20be%20sought...%20to%20reinforce%20India's%20pitch%20during%20BTA%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20industry%20official%20told%20The%20Times%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20smartphone%20export%20drive%2C%20led%20by%20Apple's%20contract%20manufacturers%2C%20has%20been%20gaining%20momentum.%20Between%20April%20and%20January%2C%20India%20exported%20nearly%20%E2%82%B91%20lakh%20crore%20worth%20of%20iPhones%2C%20up%20from%20%E2%82%B960%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20new%20tariffs%20threaten%20to%20undercut%20these%20gains%2C%20and%20India's%20production%20for%20Apple%20remains%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20real%20chance%20companies%20could%20begin%20shifting%20new%20manufacturing%20to%20countries%20with%20lower%20tariff%20exposure%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20industry%20official%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20may%20benefit%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bless%20hit%26quot%3B%20than%20others%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20long-term%20implications%20of%20the%20tariffs%20remain%20uncertain.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743790200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fkt781pug_apple-mumbai-store-reuters_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-trumps-tariffs-are-crushing-apples-make-in-india-dream-8089369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20is%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner%2C%20accounting%20for%2018%25%20of%20total%20goods%20exports.%20The%2026%25%20tariff%20could%20severely%20affect%20electronics%20shipments%2C%20profitability%2C%20and%20supply%20chains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-trumps-tariffs-are-crushing-apples-make-in-india-dream-8089369%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Homegrown%20Trainer%20Aircraft%20'Hansa%20NG'%20Set%20To%20Soar%20Higher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20aviation%20sector%20is%20booming%20with%20over%2010%20crore%20passengers%20flying%20every%20year.%20To%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demand%2C%20India%20needs%20at%20least%2030%2C000%20new%20pilots%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20pilots%20are%20currently%20trained%20in%20foreign%20planes.%20However%2C%20today%20a%20new%20Indian%20bird%20has%20come%20into%20the%20market%2C%20namely%20Hansa%20Next%20Generation%20trainer%20plane%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%20which%20will%20help%20in%20training%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScience%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20and%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20K%20Rammohan%20Naidu%20announced%20a%20new%20private%20sector%20partnership%20between%20Pioneer%20Clean%20Amps%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20makes%20about%20110%20of%20these%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20Minister%20K%20Ramomohan%20Naidu%20said%2010%20crore%20passengers%20are%20flying%20every%20year%20with%20just%20840%20aircraft%2C%20and%20the%20aviation%20industry%20has%20ordered%20another%201%2C700%20planes.%20To%20service%20them%2C%20some%2030%2C000%20new%20pilots%20will%20be%20required.%20Hansa%20NG%20offers%20a%20domestic%20solution%20to%20this%20booming%20sector%2C%20he%20added%2C%20especially%20because%20very%20soon%20India%20will%20have%20300%20airports%20from%20today's%20159.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHansa%20NG%20is%20a%20world%20class%20plane%20with%20a%20Make%20in%20India%20welcome%20twist%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Naidu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHansa%20NG%20is%20an%20indigenous%20two-seater%20trainer%20aircraft%2C%20made%20by%20CSIR-National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%20in%20Bengaluru.%20It%20costs%20about%20Rs%202%20crore%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20imported%20planes.%20Hansa%20NG%20could%20help%20fulfil%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20dream%20of%20%26quot%3Bhawai%20chappal%20to%20hawai%20udan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20A%20Pashilkar%2C%20Director%2C%20CSIR-NAL%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BHansa%20NG%20is%20the%20first%20aircraft%20designed%20and%20produced%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSIR-National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%20(NAL)%2C%20a%20constituent%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)%2C%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Minister%2C%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20developed%20HANSA-3%20(NG)%20trainer%20aircraft%20for%20commercial%20pilot%20licensing%20(CPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20offers%20a%20digital%20display%20(glass%20cockpit)%20system%20and%20is%20powered%20by%20an%20advanced%20fuel-efficient%20Rotax%20912%20iSc3%20Sports%20engine%2C%20bubble%20canopy%20with%20a%20cabin%20width%20of%2043%20inches.%20It%20is%20equipped%20with%20electrically%20operated%20flaps%20to%20meet%20the%20user's%20requirements.%20It%20offers%20excellent%20aircraft%20performance%20with%20a%20higher%20range%20of%20620%20nautical%20miles%2C%207%20hours%20endurance%2C%20and%20a%20maximum%20cruise%20speed%20of%2098%20knots%20calibrated%20airspeed%20(KCAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fcs3b7ck8_hansa-ng_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitendra%20Singh%20said%20the%20aircraft%20can%20also%20be%20used%20for%20surveillance%20purposes%20and%20environmental%20monitoring.%20In%20fact%2C%20NAL%20is%20also%20making%20an%20all-electric%20version%20of%20the%20Hansa%20plane%20in%20view%20of%20the%20concerns%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSIR-NAL%20has%20embarked%20upon%20the%20design%20and%20development%20of%20the%20Electric-HANSA%20(E-HANSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN%20Kalaiselvi%2C%20Secretary%2C%20DSIR%20and%20Director%20General%2C%20CSIR%20complementing%20the%20scientists%20said%20the%20successful%20flying%20demonstration%20of%20HANSA-3(NG)%20at%20the%20recent%20Aero%20India%202025%20shows%20the%20commitment%20of%20CSIR%20towards%20the%20national%20need%20of%20developing%20indigenous%20technologies%20to%20the%20end%20customers%20like%20Flying%20Training%20Organizations%20(FTOs)%20to%20ensure%20a%20complete%20ecosystem%20for%20successful%20commercialization%20of%20CSIR%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20meet%20the%20domestic%20demand%20as%20well%20as%20export%20potential%2C%20CSIR%20NAL%20has%20teamed%20up%20with%20the%20industry%20partner%20Pioneer%20Clean%20Amps%20Pvt%20Ltd.%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20will%20aim%20to%20set%20up%20its%20manufacturing%20facility%20to%20build%20about%2036%20aircraft%20per%20year%2C%20and%20gradually%20upscale%20to%2072%20aircraft%20per%20year%2C%20furthering%20the%20aims%20and%20objectives%20of%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitendra%20Singh%20praised%20the%20efforts%20of%20scientists%20for%20the%20successful%20demonstration%20and%20commercialization%20of%20the%20indigenous%20HANSA-3(NG)%20with%20the%20industry%20partner%20Pioneer%20Clean%20Amps%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20aircraft%20will%20satisfy%20the%20requirements%20of%20flying%20clubs%20for%20obtaining%20PPL%20(Private%20Pilot%20License)%20and%20CPL%20(Commercial%20Pilot%20License)%20for%20the%20young%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20large%20and%20world-class%20flying%20training%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20the%20Indian%20aviation%20sector's%20rapidly%20growing%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20availability%20of%20CSIR's%20indigenous%20HANSA-3(NG)%20aircraft%20will%20make%20India's%20aviation%20industry%20robust%20and%20to%20realise%20PM%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20leading%20aviation%20hub%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%20and%20Viksit%20Bharat%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20indigenous%20small%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20under%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20will%20further%20support%20the%20development%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20small%20and%20medium-scale%20private%20entrepreneurs%20for%20production%20of%20airworthy%20components%2C%20including%20assembly%20and%20integration%20of%20aircraft%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20will%20help%20to%20create%20employment%20opportunities%20with%20on-the-job%20training%20for%20ITI%20and%20diploma%20holders%20in%20various%20disciplines%20of%20aircraft%20building%20and%20AME%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hansa-3(NG)%20aircraft%20would%20be%20an%20affordable%20and%20appreciable%20trainer%20aircraft%20for%20the%20young%20generation%20of%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSIR-NAL%20has%20been%20in%20the%20forefront%20of%20designing%20indigenous%20civil%20aircraft%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20all%20composite%20two-seater%20HANSA-3%20ab-initio%20trainer%20aircraft%20was%20certified%20in%202000.%20Subsequently%2C%20CSIR%20in%20partnership%20with%20M%2Fs%20Mahindra%20developed%20a%205-seater%20CNM-5%20aircraft%20and%20flew%20it%20successfully.%20HANSA-NG%20(i.e.%2C%20Next%20Generation)%20was%20certified%20in%202023%20having%20advanced%20glass%20cockpit%2C%20bubble%20canopy%20and%20improved%20fuel%20efficiency%20comparable%20to%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743790200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fdec7m75g_hansa-ng_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-homegrown-trainer-aircraft-hansa-ng-set-to-soar-higher-8089420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20aviation%20sector%20is%20booming%20with%20over%2010%20crore%20passengers%20flying%20every%20year.%20To%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demand%2C%20India%20needs%20at%20least%2030%2C000%20new%20pilots%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-homegrown-trainer-aircraft-hansa-ng-set-to-soar-higher-8089420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Fires%20National%20Security%20Agency%20Director%20Timothy%20Haugh%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20fired%20General%20Timothy%20Haugh%20as%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency%2C%20in%20a%20national%20security%20purge%20that%20sources%20said%20on%20Friday%20included%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20staff%20at%20the%20White%20House%20national%20security%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSA%20director%20Air%20Force%20General%20Haugh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20head%20of%20US%20Cyber%20Command%2C%20was%20dismissed%20along%20with%20Wendy%20Noble%2C%20his%20deputy%20at%20the%20NSA%2C%20two%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20decision%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20sources%20said%20at%20least%2010%20staff%20were%20let%20go%20at%20the%20NSC%2C%20along%20with%20four%20senior%20directors%2C%20including%20the%20entire%20International%20Organization%20(IO)%20Directorate%2C%20which%20works%20with%20international%20and%20multilateral%20groups%20like%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20reason%20was%20given%20for%20the%20firings%2C%20which%20took%20place%20after%20the%20Republican%20president%20had%20an%20Oval%20Office%20meeting%20with%20Laura%20Loomer%2C%20a%20far-right%20political%20activist%20known%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20theorist%2C%20who%20said%20on%20X.com%20she%20had%20given%20Trump%20a%20list%20of%20officials%20she%20considered%20disloyal%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20declined%20comment%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Trump%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20his%20administration%20staffed%20with%20those%20who%20support%20his%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20always%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20people%20-%20people%20we%20don't%20like%20or%20people%20that%20take%20advantage%20of%2C%20or%20people%20that%20may%20have%20loyalties%20to%20someone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IO%20directorate%20at%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20works%20with%20international%20and%20multilateral%20groups%2C%20including%20the%20UN%20and%20Group%20of%20Seven.%20FBI%20Director%20Kash%20Patel%20formerly%20served%20in%20the%20directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20terms%2C%20Trump%20has%20deprioritized%20his%20administration's%20participation%20in%20some%20of%20these%20groups%2C%20focusing%20instead%20on%20an%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20first%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSC%20firings%20also%20included%20Daniel%20Gastfriend%20and%20Tim%20Sheeran%2C%20both%20directors%20with%20the%20health%20security%20and%20biodefense%20directorate%2C%20two%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20outlets%20including%20The%20Washington%20Post%20had%20reported%20Haugh's%20firing%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20citing%20current%20and%20former%20US%20officials%2C%20who%20said%20they%20did%20not%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20Haugh's%20dismissal%20or%20Noble's%20reassignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoble%20was%20reassigned%20to%20a%20job%20within%20the%20Pentagon's%20office%20of%20the%20Undersecretary%20of%20Defense%20for%20Intelligence%2C%20the%20Post%20said.%20The%20NSA%20is%20part%20of%20the%20US%20Defense%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Cyber%20Command%20deputy%20William%20Hartmann%20was%20named%20acting%20NSA%20director%20and%20Sheila%20Thomas%2C%20who%20was%20executive%20director%20at%20the%20NSA%2C%20was%20named%20acting%20deputy%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHAUGH%20WAS%20NOT%20ON%20THE%20SIGNAL%20CHAT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20criticized%20the%20firings%2C%20saying%20they%20represented%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentative%20Jim%20Himes%2C%20a%20Connecticut%20Democrat%20who%20is%20ranking%20member%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20Intelligence%20Committee%2C%20denounced%20the%20firings%20and%20asked%20for%20an%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20known%20General%20Haugh%20to%20be%20an%20honest%20and%20forthright%20leader%20who%20followed%20the%20law%20and%20put%20national%20security%20first%20-%20I%20fear%20those%20are%20precisely%20the%20qualities%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20his%20firing%20in%20this%20Administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Himes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenate%20Intelligence%20Committee%20Vice%20Chairman%20Mark%20Warner%2C%20a%20Virginia%20Democrat%2C%20noted%20that%2C%20unlike%20some%20other%20top%20Trump%20administration%20officials%2C%20Haugh%20was%20not%20on%20a%20discussion%20of%20military%20plans%20on%20the%20Signal%20commercial%20messaging%20app%20that%20inadvertently%20included%20a%20magazine%20journalist%2C%20raising%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20astonishing%2C%20too%2C%20that%20President%20Trump%20would%20fire%20the%20nonpartisan%2C%20experienced%20leader%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency%20while%20still%20failing%20to%20hold%20any%20member%20of%20his%20team%20accountable%20for%20leaking%20classified%20information%20on%20a%20commercial%20messaging%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20said%20in%20his%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20a%20Republican%2C%20has%20fired%20multiple%20nonpartisan%20top%20officials%20at%20US%20agencies%20and%20installed%20loyalists%20since%20beginning%20his%20second%20term%20on%20Jan.%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20he%20fired%20Air%20Force%20General%20C.Q.%20Brown%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%2C%20who%20was%20dismissed%20al