20%26quot%3BWe%20work%20every%20day%20to%20build%20a%20foundation%20so%20that%20we%20can%20stand%20on%20our%20own%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20there%20yet.%20What%20he%20(Rubio)%20says%20doesn't%20hold%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20made%20Greenland's%20takeover%20a%20top%20priority%20and%20a%20strategic%20foreign%20policy%20goal%20-%20for%20which%20it%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20a%20military%20offensive%20either.%20When%20Donald%20Trump%20first%20suggested%20that%20he%20wants%20the%20US%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuy%26quot%3B%20Greenland%2C%20it%20was%20taken%20as%20a%20joke%2C%20but%20over%20the%20weeks%20and%20months%20the%20world%20understood%20that%20there%20is%20no%20humour%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenmark%2C%20whose%20semi-autonomous%20territory%20Greenland%20does%20not%20have%20the%20diplomatic%20or%20military%20might%20to%20stand%20up%20to%20the%20US%2C%20has%20come%20to%20its%20rescue.%20But%20they%20too%20are%20feeling%20the%20pressure.%20Danish%20PM%20Mette%20Frederiksen%20today%20accused%20the%20US%20of%20subjecting%20Denmark%20and%20Greenland%20to%20immense%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20and%20threats%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20firmly%20rejected%20US'%20attempts%20to%20annex%20Greenland%2C%20citing%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20annex%20other%20countries%20-%20not%20even%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20international%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Frederiksen%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20top%20Greenlandic%20officials%20in%20Nuuk%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Greenland.%20%26quot%3BNational%20borders%2C%20sovereignty%2C%20territorial%20integrity%20-%20these%20are%20rooted%20in%20international%20law.%20These%20principles%20were%20established%20after%20World%20War%20II%20so%20that%20small%20countries%20would%20not%20have%20to%20fear%20large%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20seek%20to%20take%20over%20part%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20(of%20Denmark)'s%20territory%2C%20when%20we%20are%20subjected%20to%20pressure%20and%20threats%20by%20our%20closest%20ally%2C%20what%20are%20we%20to%20think%20about%20the%20country%20we%20have%20admired%20for%20so%20many%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Frederiksen%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Denmark%20and%20Greenland%20have%2C%20for%20long%2C%20been%20close%20allies%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20US%20also%20has%20a%20strategic%20military%20and%20nuclear%20missile%20base%20in%20Greenland.%20But%20President%20Trump's%20threats%20of%20annexing%20the%20arctic%20island%20rich%20in%20natural%20and%20mineral%20resources%2C%20has%20led%20to%20widespread%20anti-US%20sentiment%20and%20resentment%20against%20the%20Trump%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Greenlanders%20held%20the%20largest-ever%20protests%20in%20the%20island's%20history%20against%20the%20US.%20Just%20hours%20ahead%20of%20a%20visit%20by%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20last%20month%2C%20Greenland%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20autonomous%20government.%20Four%20political%20parties%2C%20representing%2023%20of%20the%2031%20seats%20in%20Greenland's%20Parliament%2C%20signed%20a%20historic%20coalition%20agreement%20to%20establish%20the%20new%20government.%20Jens-Frederik%20Nielsen%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Demokraatit%20(Democratic%20Party)%2C%20will%20serve%20as%20prime%20minister.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743789300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fl5qravvc_donald-trump-afp_625x300_04_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-wedges-its-way-in-says-greenland-does-not-want-to-be-part-of-denmark-8089326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Greenland%20and%20Denmark%2C%20of%20which%20it%20is%20a%20part%2C%20have%20vociferously%20rejected%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20buyout%26quot%3B%20proposal%2C%20Washington%20has%20struck%20ba