%20by%20Planet%20Labs%20PBC%20shows%20six%20American%20B-2%20bomber%20planes%20in%20Diego%20Garcia%20(AFP%20Photo)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fahufd8mc_us-b2-stealth-bombers-b2-bombers-diego-garcia-afp_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3EThis%20satellite%20image%20by%20Planet%20Labs%20PBC%20shows%20six%20American%20B-2%20bomber%20planes%20in%20Diego%20Garcia%20(AFP%20Photo)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20the%20US%20has%20also%20planned%20to%20increase%20its%20aircraft%20carrier%20presence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20from%20one%20to%20three%20-%20two%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20one%20in%20the%20western%20Pacific%2C%20near%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20planned%20for%20the%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20to%20head%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20while%20the%20USS%20Harry%20S.%20Truman%20will%20continue%20ops%20from%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20The%20third%20aircraft%20carrier%20-%20the%20USS%20Nimitz%20and%20its%20carrier%20strike%20group%20fleet%20will%20move%20towards%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20not%20the%20end%20of%20US'%20massive%20deployment%20surrounding%20Asia.%20Pentagon%20spokesperson%20Sean%20Parnell%20said%20that%20US%20Secretary%20of%20Defence%20Peter%20Hegseth%20has%20%26quot%3Balso%20ordered%20the%20deployment%20of%20additional%20squadrons%20and%20other%20air%20assets%20that%20will%20further%20reinforce%20our%20defensive%20air-support%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%20He%20however%2C%20did%20not%20elaborate%20what%20these%20squadrons%20or%20assets%20would%20comprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20THE%20SUDDEN%20MASSIVE%20DEPLOYMENT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20sudden%20and%20massive%20military%20deployment%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20justified%20it%20saying%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20done%20to%20improve%20America's%20defensive%20posture%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20United%20States%20and%20its%20partners%20remain%20committed%20to%20regional%20security%2C%20and%20are%20prepared%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20state%20or%20non-state%20actor%20seeking%20to%20broaden%20or%20escalate%20conflict%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYEMEN%20AND%20THE%20HOUTHIS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20no%20country%20or%20terrorist%20organisation%20was%20named%20directly%2C%20several%20defence%20analysts%20point%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20south%20Asia%20-%20especially%20Iran%20and%20Yemen.%20Over%20the%20last%20fortnight%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20steadily%20increased%20military%20action%20against%20the%20Yemen-based%20Houthis%20-%20a%20militant%20group%20backed%20by%20Iran%20-%20which%20has%20been%20targeting%20American%20merchant%20and%20military%20ships%20over%20US'%20support%20to%20Israel.%20Iran%20and%20all%20its%20%26quot%3Bproxies%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20supporting%20Hamas%20-%20a%20US-designated%20terror%20organisation%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20at%20war%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20defence%20experts%20say%20that%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20US%20military%20deployment%20is%20far%20too%20big%20to%20be%20just%20for%20the%20Houthis%20or%20for%20Iran.%20They%20argue%20that%20two%20B-2%20bombers%20-%20each%20with%20a%20payload%20capacity%20of%2040%2C000%20pounds%20-%20would%20have%20been%20more%20than%20sufficient%20to%20tackle%20the%20militants%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20openly%20warned%20the%20Houthis%20and%20its%20backers%20in%20Iran.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social%2C%20President%20Trump%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BStop%20shooting%20at%20US%20ships%2C%20and%20we%20will%20stop%20shooting%20at%20you.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20have%20only%20just%20begun%2C%20and%20the%20real%20pain%20is%20yet%20to%20come%2C%20for%20both%20the%20Houthis%20and%20their%20sponsors%20in%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIRAN'S%20NUCLEAR%20FACILITIES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20month%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20mounted%20pressure%20on%20Iran%20to%20renegotiate%20its%20nuclear%20deal%20-%20a%20move%20that%20Tehran%20has%20outrightly%20rejected.%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20Fox%20News%20last%20month%2C%20President%20Trump%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20ways%20Iran%20can%20be%20handled%3A%20militarily%2C%20or%20you%20make%20a%20deal.%20I%20would%20prefer%20to%20make%20a%20deal%2C%20because%20I'm%20not%20looking%20to%20hurt%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20made%20the%20US%20exit%20what%20he%20had%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20nuclear%20deal%26quot%3B%20with%20Iran%20during%20his%20first%20term.%20He%20now%20wants%20Iran%20to%20engage%20in%20talks%20in%20order%20to%20bring%20a%20new%20and%20improved%20nuclear%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%202017-2021%20term%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20withdrew%20from%20a%202015%20deal%20between%20Iran%20and%20world%20powers%20that%20placed%20strict%20limits%20on%20Tehran's%20disputed%20nuclear%20activities%20in%20exchange%20for%20sanctions%20relief.%20President%20Trump%20also%20reimposed%20sweeping%20US%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20then%2C%20Iran%20has%20far%20surpassed%20that%20deal's%20limits%20on%20uranium%20enrichment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20now%20wants%20a%20new%20deal%2C%20and%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20the%20use%20of%20force.%20Washington%20may%20consider%20destroying%20Iran's%20nuclear%20facilities%20and%20labs%2C%20and%20thereby%20finish%20off%20Iran's%20nuclear%20weapons%20programme%2C%20should%20Tehran%20not%20be%20willing%20to%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Iran%2C%20Pentagon%20spokesperson%20Sean%20Parnell%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Secretary%20of%20Defence%20continues%20to%20make%20clear%20that%2C%20should%20Iran%20or%20its%20proxies%20threaten%20American%20personnel%20and%20interests%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20United%20States%20will%20take%20decisive%20action%20to%20defend%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%20Though%20he%20did%20not%20mention%20anything%20about%20nuclear%20talks%20with%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECHINA%20AND%20RUSSIA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20massive%20deployment%20of%20America's%20most%20advanced%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20bombers%2C%20and%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20is%20also%20aimed%20at%20sending%20a%20signal%20to%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20who%20are%20Iran's%20allies%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington's%20move%20to%20deploy%20the%20USS%20Nimitz%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20in%20the%20western%20Pacific%20also%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20Beijing%20that%20the%20US%20is%20serious%20about%20safeguarding%20its%20interest%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20deployment%20of%20the%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20sends%20a%20similar%20message%20to%20Moscow.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743785640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjev23f2s_us-b2-stealth-bombers-b2-bombers-diego-garcia-afp_625x300_04_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-moves-largest-b-2-stealth-bomber-fleet-3-aircraft-carriers-to-indo-pacific-8088789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20world%20was%20busy%20figuring%20out%20Donald%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariff%20move%20and%20its%20fallout%2C%20the%20United%20States%20quietly%20made%20a%20massive%20military%20move%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-moves-largest-b-2-stealth-bomber-fleet-3-aircraft-carriers-to-indo-pacific-8088789%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7