49.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUsing%20Parliament%20Majority%20To%20Take%20Muslims'%20Rights%26quot%3B%3A%20A%20Owaisi%20On%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20chief%20and%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20contentions%20of%20Mr%20Owaisi%20was%20the%20inclusion%20of%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20Waqf%20councils%20and%20state%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20also%20said%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20using%20their%20majority%20in%20parliament%20not%20to%20reform%2C%20but%20to%20destroy%20and%20take%20away%20the%20rights%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20If%20you%20see%20the%20central%20Waqf%20council%2C%20out%20of%20the%2022%20members%2C%2011%20can%20be%20and%20will%20be%20non-Muslims%3B%2010%20have%20to%20be%20Muslims.%20That%20is%20what%20the%20bill%20says.%20You%20come%20to%20the%20state%20Waqf%20board%20formation%20-%20out%20of%2011%2C%20compulsory%20four%20have%20to%20be%20Muslims.%20The%20remaining%20can%20and%20will%20be%20non-Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20basically%2C%20you%20will%20be%20managing%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Endowment%20Board%2C%20the%20Jain%20Endowment%20Board%2C%20or%20the%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee.%20That%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20grave%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution...%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20was%20misleading%20deliberately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20his%20politics%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20regressive%20if%20he%20opposes%20what%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20an%20important%20reform%20measure%2C%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20using%20your%20majority%20in%20parliament%20not%20to%20reform%2C%20but%20to%20destroy%2C%20to%20take%20away%20all%20the%20rights%20Muslims%20have%3B%20you%20are%20by%20enacting%20a%20law%20waging%20a%20war%20on%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contentious%20Section%2040%20and%20allegations%20over%20mismanagement%20of%20Waqf%20lands%2C%20the%20AIMIM%20chief%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20joint%20working%20committee%20and%20I%20can%20share%20with%20you%20right%20now%20that%20when%20I%20had%20asked%20this%20particular%20question%20along%20with%20other%20members%20about%20this%20so-called%20misuse%20of%20Section%2040%2C%20you%20know%20the%20reply%20we%20got%20was%20that%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20Section%2040%20was%20used%20only%20518%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%20that%2C%20only%20eight%20people%20have%20gone%20to%20court.%20Now%20that%20same%20Section%2040%20provision%20exists%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Endowment%20Board%2C%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Endowment%20Boards...%20In%20one%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20accepted%20that%20with%20the%20use%20of%20Section%2040%2C%20a%20property%20was%20saved...%20You%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Tribunal%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20the%20courts%2C%20who's%20stopping%20you%20from%20doing%20that%3F%20But%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20you%20take%20away%2C%20remove%20Section%2040.%20You%20might%20be%20having%20a%20genuine%20grievance%2C%20but%20to%20get%20a%20particular%20section%20omitted%2C%20that%20is%20completely%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20part%20of%20his%20speech%20in%20parliament%20was%20on%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%2C%20which%20limited%20the%20Waqf%20Tribunal's%20ability%20to%20recognise%20properties%20based%20on%20historical%20usage.%20To%20a%20related%20question%20on%20how%20will%20a%20timestamp%20on%20a%20property%20based%20on%20its%20usage%20for%20several%20decades%20address%20a%20conflict%20like%20this%2C%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20illegal%20for%20a%20government%20to%20completely%20overturn%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment...%20If%20as%20a%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20I%20cannot%20use%20'Waqf%20by%20use'%20against%20the%20government%2C%20where%20will%20I%20use%20it%3F%20The%20same%20provision%20exists%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Endowment%20Board...%20You%20are%20denying%20everything%20to%20me%2C%20then%20how%20can%20I%20protect%20my%20property%3F%20You%20have%20created%20a%20mechanism%20in%20which%20the%20definition%20of%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%20has%20been%20completely%20modified%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20more%20fruitful%20legislation%20would%20have%20come%26quot%3B%20had%20the%20debate%20been%20for%20another%20four-five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20week%2C%20we're%20sitting%20for%20four%20days%2C%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20every%20day.%20I%20must%20give%20credit%20to%20all%20the%20members%20(MPs)%2C%20irrespective%20of%20which%20party%20we%20belong%20to.%20But%20you%20%5Bruling%20alliance%20MPs%5D%20were%20pushing%20us...%20The%20government%20was%20not%20ready%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20to%20listen%20to%20our%20viewpoint%2C%20to%20accept%20all%20these%20issues.%20They%20just%20wanted%20to%20bulldoze%20and%20have%20their%20say.%20Now%20they%20have%20created%20an%20unconstitutional%20legislation%2C%20which%20will%20be%20challenged%20and%20which%20will%20be%20rejected%20by%20the%20right-thinking%20people%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AIMIM%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20leader%20who%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20proposed%20law%20is%20Congress%20