%2C%20the%20police%20found%20the%20skeleton%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20Bettadarapura%20(Periyapatna%20taluk)%20and%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20in%20court%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20skeleton%20belonged%20to%20Mallige%20and%20that%20Suresh%20had%20murdered%20her.%20He%20was%20then%20jailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%201%2C%20Mallige%20was%20found%20in%20Madikeri%20by%20a%20friend%20of%20Suresh%2C%20who%20saw%20her%20with%20another%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Fifth%20Additional%20District%20and%20Sessions%20Court%2C%20and%20she%20was%20subsequently%20produced%20before%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20police's%20lapses%2C%20the%20court%20on%20Thursday%20directed%20the%20SP%20to%20submit%20a%20complete%20report%20on%20the%20case%20by%20April%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Suresh's%20advocate%2C%20Pandu%20Poojari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuresh%2C%20who%20is%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Kushalnagar%2C%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20in%202020%20at%20the%20Kushalnagar%20Rural%20Police%20Station%20regarding%20his%20wife's%20disappearance.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20skeleton%20was%20found%20within%20the%20Bettadarapura%20police%20station%20limits.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20Bettadarapura%20police%20arrested%20Suresh%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20killed%20his%20wife%20over%20an%20illicit%20affair.%20A%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20him.%26quot%3B%20The%20police%20had%20sent%20the%20skeleton%20for%20a%20DNA%20test%20along%20with%20blood%20samples%20from%20Mallige's%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20before%20the%20DNA%20report%20came%2C%20the%20police%20filed%20the%20final%20charge%20sheet%20in%20court.%20Later%2C%20though%20he%20got%20bail%2C%20the%20DNA%20test%20report%20that%20eventually%20came%20showed%20a%20mismatch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20discharge%20application%20was%20filed%20citing%20the%20DNA%20mismatch%2C%20the%20court%20did%20not%20accept%20it%20and%20asked%20for%20witness%20examination%2C%20including%20that%20of%20Mallige's%20mother%20and%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20deposed%20before%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20alive%20and%20had%20eloped%20with%20someone.%20The%20court%20questioned%20the%20Kushalnagar%20and%20Bettadarapura%20police%20about%20the%20loopholes%20in%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20but%20they%20defended%20their%20investigation%20and%20maintained%20that%20the%20skeleton%20belonged%20to%20Mallige%20and%20that%20Suresh%20had%20murdered%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advocate%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20April%201%2C%20Mallige%20was%20found%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Madikeri%2C%20having%20a%20meal%20with%20a%20man.%20She%20was%20spotted%20by%20Suresh's%20friend%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20witness%20named%20in%20the%20charge%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Madikeri%20police%20station%2C%20following%20which%20an%20%26quot%3Badvancement%20application%26quot%3B%20was%20filed%20before%20the%20district%20judge's%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%2C%20treating%20the%20matter%20seriously%2C%20asked%20police%20to%20produce%20her%20immediately.%20She%20was%20then%20presented%20in%20court.%20When%20questioned%2C%20she%20admitted%20to%20eloping%20and%20marrying%20another%20man.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20unaware%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20Suresh.%20She%20had%20been%20living%20in%20a%20village%20named%20Shettyhalli%2C%20just%2025-30%20km%20from%20Madikeri%2C%20but%20police%20made%20no%20effort%20to%20trace%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20this%20a%20very%20serious%20and%20rare%20case%2C%20the%20advocate%20said%20the%20key%20questions%20before%20the%20court%20now%20are%3A%20whose%20skeleton%20was%20it%2C%20and%20why%20did%20the%20police%20file%20a%20false%20charge%20sheet%3F%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20had%20summoned%20t