%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20assert%20India's%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20Katchatheevu%20Island%20ahead%20of%20his%20visit%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor-politician%20proposed%20a%2099-year%20lease%20of%20the%20island%20as%20an%20interim%20solution%2C%20emphasising%20that%20full%20retrieval%20remains%20the%20only%20permanent%20resolution%20to%20the%20decades-long%20fishermen%20crisis.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20slammed%20both%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20for%20failing%20to%20reclaim%20Katchatheevu%2C%20calling%20the%20DMK's%20recent%20Assembly%20resolution%20-%20urging%20the%20Centre%20to%20retrieve%20the%20island-%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20drama%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%202026%20Tamil%20Nadu%20polls.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20DMK%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20in%201974%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20island's%20transfer%20to%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TVK%20leader%20also%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20discriminating%20against%20Tamil%20Nadu%20fishermen%2C%20noting%20that%20while%20their%20counterparts%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20other%20states%20receive%20protection%2C%20Tamil%20fishermen%20face%20arrests%20and%20confiscations%20by%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Navy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Katchatheevu%20retrieval%20demand%20gained%20momentum%20after%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20wrote%20to%20PM%20Modi%20on%20Friday.%20Mr%20Stalin%20sought%20a%20review%20of%20the%201974%20Indo-Lankan%20treaty%20and%20urged%20PM%20Modi%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20jailed%20fishermen%20as%20a%20goodwill%20gesture%20during%20his%20Sri%20Lanka%20visit%20-%20demands%20that%20were%20also%20included%20in%20the%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatchatheevu%2C%20a%201.9%20sq%20km%20island%2C%20lies%2012%20nautical%20miles%20off%20Rameswaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20the%20fish%20po