%2C%20there%20was%20the%20prevalent%20patriarchy.%20People%20called%20me%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhiji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20Lakshmiji.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20my%20work.%20My%20attire%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20locals.%20I%20wore%20trousers%20and%20shirts%20in%20a%20place%20where%20women%20wore%20%3Cem%3Esaris%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Egoonghats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(veils)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20liberal%20in-laws%2C%20especially%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20education%2C%20were%20a%20blessing.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20ceramic%20design%20opportunities%20in%20Udaipur%20meant%20she%20had%20to%20carve%20a%20new%20path.%20She%20began%20organising%20artist%20camps%2C%20helping%20potters%20and%20artisans%20create%20new%20products%2C%20and%20soon%20started%20working%20with%20the%20NGO%20Seva%20Mandir%2C%20designing%20visual%20communication%20tools%20for%20rural%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20have%20moved%20back%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20pursued%20ceramics%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20having%20a%20long-distance%20marriage%20just%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESketching%20periods%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20brush%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20while%20developing%20training%20materials%20for%20non-literate%20communities.%20She%20realised%20the%20visuals%20she%20was%20drawing%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20to%20school%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20way%20of%20drawing.%20So%2C%20I%20created%20a%20picture%20dictionary%20on%20how%20menstruation%2C%20abortion%2C%20and%20delivery%20should%20be%20depicted.%20That%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20our%20training%20manuals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELakshmi%20presents%20her%20picture%20dictionary%20%E2%80%94%20a%20visual%20tool%20she%20created%20to%20explain%20puberty%20and%20reproductive%20health%20to%20non-literate%20communities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20she%20received%20the%20prestigious%20MacArthur%20Fellowship%20to%20create%20reproductive%20health%20material%20for%20rural%20adolescents%2C%20and%20in%202001%2C%20she%20co-founded%20the%20NGO%20%E2%80%98Jatan%20Sansthan%E2%80%99%20with%20Dr%20Kailash%20Brijwasi.%20Her%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170476%2Findia-oscar-winner-period-documentary-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Edeepened%20during%20this%20time%2C%20especially%20around%20the%20need%20for%20safe%2C%20sustainable%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20designed%20a%20simple%20washable%20cloth%20napkin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Enada%20wala%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20pad%20(a%20pad%20with%20cloth%20ties%20or%20strings)%20%E2%80%94%20for%20girls%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wear%20underwear.%20It%20could%20be%20stitched%20from%20old%20%3Cem%3Epetticoats%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Esaris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20But%20when%20rural%20women%20began%20shifting%20to%20underwear%20by%20the%20late%202000s%2C%20her%20original%20design%20quietly%20faded%20away.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20pad%20died%20a%20quiet%20death%20once%20women%20started%20using%20underwear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20576px)%20100vw%2C%20576px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20design%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98nada%20wala%20pad%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20made%20from%20upcycled%20cloth%20with%20ties.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748.jpg%20576w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748-500x329.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748-150x99.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417337%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20design%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98nada%20wala%20pad%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20made%20from%20upcycled%20cloth%20with%20ties.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20575px)%20100vw%2C%20575px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20early%20pad%20design%20%E2%80%94%20simple%2C%20washable%2C%20biodegradable%20%E2%80%94%20was%20made%20for%20rural%20girls%20long%20before%20pads%20became%20mainstream.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071.jpg%20575w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071-300x132.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071-500x220.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071-150x66.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417320%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22253%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20early%20pad%20design%20%E2%80%94%20simple%2C%20washable%2C%20biodegradable%20%E2%80%94%20was%20made%20for%20rural%20girls%20long%20before%20pads%20became%20mainstream.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20women%20in%20villages%20began%20using%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Elal%20kapda%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20woollen%20felt%20fabric%20which%20could%20be%20washed%20and%20reused%20for%20about%20three%20months%20until%20it%20wore%20out.%20But%20it%20was%20uncomfortable.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20troubled%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Lakshmi%20searched%20for%20better%20alternatives%2C%20the%20larger%20menstrual%20health%20space%20was%20also%20shifting.%20Arunachalam%20Muruganantham%2C%20now%20widely%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Padman%E2%80%99%2C%20began%20developing%20affordable%20disposable%20pads.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20marketed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98She%20Cup%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20was%20gaining%20attention%20in%20urban%20circles.%20But%20Lakshmi%20remained%20cautious.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable%20with%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20for%20my%20rural%20adolescents.%20The%20wearer%20has%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20place%20and%20wear%20it.%20If%20they%20have%20medical%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20access%20to%20gynaecologists%20in%20rural%20areas.%20So%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%20has%20not%20promoted%20menstrual%20cups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20design%20meant%20to%20be%20copied%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20concern%20that%20led%20to%20Project%20Uger%20in%202011.%20%E2%80%98Uger%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98new%20beginning%E2%80%99%20in%20Mewari%20%E2%80%94%20introduced%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20reusable%20menstrual%20pads%2C%20developed%20by%20Lakshmi%20while%20pursuing%20her%20PhD%20at%20IIT%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20anxious%20to%20make%20a%20pad%20that%20would%20work%20for%20women%20and%20girls%20who%20had%20started%20wearing%20underwear.%20The%20Uger%20pad%20is%20made%20entirely%20of%20cotton%20and%20is%20biodegradable%20within%20three%20to%20four%20months.%20It%20has%20straps%20so%20you%20can%20fix%20any%20cloth%20inside.%20A%20set%20of%20six%20costs%20Rs%20180%20and%20lasts%20three%20months.%20The%20insert%20cloth%20is%20extra%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-500x335.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20Uger%20pads%2C%20made%20entirely%20from%20cotton%2C%20were%20designed%20by%20Lakshmi%20to%20be%20biodegradable%20within%20months%2C%20stitched%20by%20rural%20SHGs%20and%20intentionally%20kept%20free%20of%20copyright.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-500x335.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-300x201.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-768x514.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-1536x1029.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-up_11zon-1743519143-2048x1371.jpg